summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Sixth Avenue N.W. from West Forty-fifth Street to West Fifty-fifth Street et al, in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete sidewalks under Ordinance No. 17167, creating Local Improvement District No. 1605 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
